JFK inaugural address audio (jfk.wav)
  Path: fixtures/jfk.wav
  License: public domain (US Government work); distributed via the MIT-licensed
  llama.cpp / whisper.cpp repositories

  The committed test/demo audio clip is `samples/jfk.wav` from the ggml-org
  llama.cpp / whisper.cpp projects: a public-domain excerpt of John F. Kennedy's
  1961 inaugural address. OpenASR uses it as the single fixture for examples,
  the benchmark clip, and the test suite.
